THE CHARGE OF THE TEMPORALITIE OF THE HAILL KIRKLANDIS OF QUHATSUMEVIR BENEFIOES WITHIN THIS REALM ANNEXT TO OURE SOUERANE LORDIS CR'OUN UPOUN THE NORTH SIDE OF THE WATER OF FORTH.

ABBAY OF INCHEFFRAY.

Item the Comptar chargis him with the few maill of the landis of N ethir Carnis with the manir place and salmond fisching vpoun the Water of Iran liand in the lordsehip of Incheffray and schirefdome foirsaid set in few to Robert Grahame of Thorniek extending the yeir comptit to iij li. vi s· viij d. And with the new augmentatioun of the samyne extending the yeir foirsaid to iij s. iiij d. Inde . iij li. x s.

And with the fewferme of the foure merk land of Raith als Dumfallie and landis of Garwok pertening therto extending yeirlie to liij s. iiij d. with the yeirlie augmen· tatioun theros extending to xiij s. iiij d. And of ane pairt of the Mure of Madertie extending yeirlie to xl s. with the yeirlie augmentatioun extending to iij s. iiij d. and pultre vj sauld be infeft and altogider to iij s. iiij d. All liand in the baronio of Cardney and schirefdome of Perth set in few to Anthone Murray. Inde the yeir comptit . . . . . . . vli. xiij s. iiij d.
